      "content": "idk i just dont have the time to go to the clinic right now and it’s kinda expensive. i mean it's probably just a bad sprain since there isnt any crazy deformity or anything. if i just keep it iced and elevated for like 48 hours and take some ibuprofen, do you think that'll be enough to get through it?",
